sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant F as Next.js Agent UI
    participant B as FastAPI agent router
    participant H as History store
    participant G as Gemini 2.5 Flash
    participant T as Tool registry<br/>7 typed functions
    participant D as SQLite plus saved model

    U->>F: Question, e.g. "what drives WACMR<br/>in tightening regime?"
    F->>B: POST slash api slash agent slash chat
    B->>H: Load session history
    B->>G: System prompt plus history plus tools
    activate G
    G-->>B: Function call e.g. get_regime_stats
    deactivate G
    B->>T: Dispatch run_sql or get_shap_contributions<br/>or run_counterfactual or 4 others
    T->>D: Read SHAP CSV plus query master table
    D-->>T: Result row set
    T-->>B: Structured tool result
    B->>G: Append tool result to history
    activate G
    G-->>B: Either next function call<br/>or final natural language answer
    deactivate G
    B->>H: Persist updated history
    B-->>F: Server-Sent Events stream<br/>tokens plus tool blocks
    F-->>U: Render answer plus tool invocation chips

    Note over B,G: Loop guard, max 6 iterations<br/>then forced final answer
    Note over T: Function schemas<br/>auto-generated from Python type hints
